State Regulations

The State Fire Prevention and Building Code Council, pursuant to section
375
(3)
of the Executive Law, may adopt
procedures and application forms, and charge fees for the processing and review
of materials, devices and methods of construction in order to ascertain their
acceptability under the Uniform Fire Prevention and Building
